<div id="pf4450" class="pf w4e h303" data-page-no="4450"><div class="pc pc4450 w4e h303"><div class="t m1b2 xc4 h5 y2cbd ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 5 July 29 to August 4 </div><div class="t m1885 xd3 h122 y2b4f ff3 fs48 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Ri teousness </div><div class="t m719 xc3 h122 y2444 ff3 fs48 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">by </div><div class="t m911 x7c h122 y2444 ff3 fs48 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">.</div><div class="t m1bc7 x42 h122 y2444 ff3 fs48 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">th </div><div class="t m645 x15 h5 yfb6 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;I will greatly rejoice in the Lord, my </div><div class="t m3e5 xb7 h5 y8cb ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">soul shall be joyful in my God; for he </div><div class="t m3e0 xb7 h5 y539 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">hath clothed me with the garments of </div><div class="t m113c xb7 h5 y6fc ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">salvation, he hath covered me with the </div><div class="t m3c1 xb7 h5 y765 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">robe of righteousness&quot; (Isa. 61:10). </div><div class="t m54e x15 h35 ya42 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Ellen White tells us that the subject </div><div class="t m425 xb7 h35 y131e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of righteousness by faith should </div><div class="t m9c6 xb7 h35 y81f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">supersede all others. (See </div><div class="t m39e x96 h35 y81f ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Testimonies </div><div class="t m586 x0 h35 y7ac ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to Ministers, </div><div class="t m226 x55 h35 y7ac ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. 468.) It is the very heart </div><div class="t m2bc xb7 h35 y661 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the gospel of Jesus. It forms the </div><div class="t m7b6 xb7 h35 y4ab ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">foundation of every other aspect of </div><div class="t m171a xb7 h35 y1ba ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the truth. </div><div class="t m9d5 x27 h35 y8b5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Once in a while someone claims to </div><div class="t m1a0 xb7 h35 yb6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">be a pioneer in the presentation of the </div><div class="t m71d xb7 h35 y11d9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">truth of the righteousness of Christ. </div><div class="t md6 xb7 h35 y102 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">But the message has been in the Bible </div><div class="t mc6d xb7 h35 y4e6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">from the time it was written, and its </div><div class="t m2d3 xb7 h35 y59d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">light has been flashing in the inspired </div><div class="t m61c xb7 h35 ya49 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">writings of Ellen White almost from the </div><div class="t m9a7 xb7 h35 y3d8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">beginning of her career as a </div><div class="t m197 xb9 h35 yd5e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">messenger of the Lord. </div><div class="t m7a6 x27 h35 y127d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">It is true that for some time, and </div><div class="t m30c xb9 h35 yc0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">especially before 1888, our church was </div><div class="t m1a0 xb9 h35 y4b4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">inclined to stress obedience to the law </div><div class="t m78b xb9 h35 y14bc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">on a legalistic basis. Thus many of our </div><div class="t m527 xb9 h35 y1044 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">brethren lost sight of the truth that </div><div class="t ma0 xb9 h35 y52a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">righteousness and salvation are to be </div><div class="t m83c xb9 h35 y72c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">received by faith alone, by a full </div><div class="t m195a xb9 h35 y90e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">recognition of our need and our </div><div class="t m177 xb9 h35 yf4d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">impotency, and by a total dependence </div><div class="t m5d0 xb9 h35 y7bd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">on our Saviour and our surrender to </div><div class="t m15e xb9 h35 y2b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Him. But at the General Conference of </div><div class="t m188 xb7 h35 yfec ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1888, with the presentation of this </div><div class="t m3e2 xb9 h35 y2e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">subject, and also with the continuing </div><div class="t m86 xb9 h35 ya7e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">efforts of many of the leaders of this </div><div class="t m9fb xb9 h35 y3f6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">movement, the picture has been </div><div class="t m6f4 xb9 h35 y70d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">changed. From that year until our own </div><div class="t m2e8 xb9 h35 y7c4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">days the glorious truth that man is </div><div class="t mde3 x3 h35 ya9f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">justified and also sanctified by faith in </div><div class="t m425 xb9 h35 y3e5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Christ and by a complete reliance on </div><div class="t m7ed xb9 h35 y9a8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Him has been like a struggling light  </div><div class="t m7f9 x20 h35 yfe8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">increasing in brilliance; it has not been </div><div class="t m6b8 x20 h35 y17c8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">easy—the light is continually fighting </div><div class="t m5a6 x20 h35 y539 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to keep from being extinguished. This </div><div class="t m8d6 x58 h35 y6fc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">light must illuminate the whole world, </div><div class="t m2f1 x58 h35 y765 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">since the righteousness of Christ is the </div><div class="t m60a x20 h35 y8ed ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">third angel&apos;s message in verity. (See </div><div class="t m243 x20 h35 ya42 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Evangelism, </div><div class="t m110a xa6 h35 ya42 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. 190.) </div><div class="t m813 x21 h35 y131f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The righteousness of Christ is both </div><div class="t m4aa x58 h35 y81f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">imputed and imparted. Justification is </div><div class="t m11b x58 h35 y7ac ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">by faith in Christ and sanctification is </div><div class="t m8d3 x58 h35 y661 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">by faith in Christ. The one is </div><div class="t m8d3 x20 h35 y4ab ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">forgiveness of sin; and the other is </div><div class="t me19 x58 h35 y7f1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">victory over sin. </div><div class="t m3af x21 h35 y1011 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">These expressions—imputed and </div><div class="t m7ba x58 h35 yb6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">imparted righteousness—do not </div><div class="t me7a x58 h35 y11d9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">designate two classes of </div><div class="t m16f x58 h35 y9f5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">righteousness. There is just one saving </div><div class="t m9cc x58 h35 y4e6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">righteousness: it is the righteousness </div><div class="t me97 x58 h35 y9ac ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of Christ. It manifests itself in two </div><div class="t m4a3 x58 h35 ya32 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">different aspects, both indispensable </div><div class="t mad7 x58 h35 y3d8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">but not interchangeable. And the only </div><div class="t m54a x58 h35 yd5e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">way of securing that righteousness in </div><div class="t m6e9 x58 h35 y8bf ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">either of its two aspects, is• by faith. </div><div class="t m14a x58 h5 y2e7 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m23f x58 h5 y10d ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t mca x7 h5 yd41 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Need of Righteousness </div><div class="t m310 x7 h5 ye8b ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Job 25:4) </div><div class="t m558 x58 h5 yc56 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m65e x7 h5 yc56 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Man&apos;s Method Versus God&apos;s </div><div class="t m119c x7 h5 y72c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Method </div><div class="t ma95 x7 h5 y3ad ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Phil. 3:8, 9) </div><div class="t mb7 x58 h5 ya06 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m7f3 x7 h5 ya06 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Imputed Righteousness </div><div class="t m9c6 x7 h5 y7be ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rom. 3:24, 25, 28) </div><div class="t m1ce x58 h5 y2b ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m119f x7 h5 y89b ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Imparted Righteousness </div><div class="t m1e1 x7 h5 yfed ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(1 John 5:4) </div><div class="t m8a8 x58 h5 y2e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m36e x7 h5 yf52 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Partakers of the Divine Nature </div><div class="t m1ed x7 h5 y115b ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(John 8:11</div><div class="t mf82 xa0 h35 ya7e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">.</div><div class="t m568 xa2 h5 ya7e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">) </div><div class="t m2ef x1c h5 yf54 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m359 xae h5 y3f6 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How to Secure Christ&apos;s </div><div class="t m1578 x7 h5 y115c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Righteousness </div><div class="t m9b6 xae h5 y7c4 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Gal. 2:20) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
